content: Hi, I definitely don’t want to bug staff with this but supposedly there are some volunteer-created Harris-Walz Zoom backgrounds out there, and I am hoping to have one for my chat captain shift later this evening! I’m not looking for anything too distracting or with pictures, just a basic blue or very simple pattern that maybe says Harris-Walz or 2024 Victory or something like that in the corner. My current Zoom background is really sad, and I only see phone backgrounds available for download on the merch store!
Hey Holly- Just threw a few of these together for your zoom backgrounds!
and just for fun, here is a version of the digital yard sign as a zoom background!
Hi Holly! We are working on it right now! I’m going to show the designs we have to my boss for approval and then if they’re approved we should have them shortly for all vote team folks to use!
Oh excellent thank you! I'll wait to hear further.
